39.5"/><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0" ss:Height="135" ss:StyleID="s63"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">SECTORDEFINITIONS_STRATEGIC_DLC03</Data></Cell><Cell ss:Index="3" ss:StyleID="s62"/><Cell ss:StyleID="s62"/><Cell ss:Index="7" ss:StyleID="s62"><Data ss:Type="String">The DEV TEAM / MISC NOTES column contains info on what text between { } signs means (if applicable). It usually stands for either a numeric value, or a numeric value with an icon. Text between [ ] signs stands for a certain type of icon. </Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="s62"/><Cell ss:StyleID="s62"/></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">SCENE ID</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">TEXT ID</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">ENGLISH STRING</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">LOCALIZED STRING</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">ALTERNATIVE ENGLISH STRING</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">ALTERNATIVE LOCALIZED STRING</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">LOCALIZATION NOTES</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">DEV TEAM / MISC NOTES</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">OLD TEXT</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">SECTOR_FEATURE_ARTIFICIAL_FERTILITY</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Artificially Fertile</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Sztuczne nawożenie</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0" ss:Height="30"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">SECTOR_FEATURE_ARTIFICIAL_FERTILITY</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">This sector has been artificially fertilized.[br/]Grants {DeltaSupply}[supply/] to the colony it is linked to.</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Ten sektor został użyźniony sztucznymi nawozami.[br/]Daje {DeltaSupply}[supply/] kolonii, z którą jest połączony.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:Index="7"><Data ss:Type="String">Delta supply means food.</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0" ss:Height="45"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">SECTOR_FEATURE_ARTIFICIAL_FERTILITY</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">FLAVOUR</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Terratech's control over the climates and biospheres of the Star Union worlds can still be felt long after they are gone. Exceptionally fertile sectors like this are often a sign of past involvement by Terratech.</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Kontrola Terratechu nad klimatem i biosferami planet Związku Gwiezdnego jest nadal odczuwalna, mimo że od upadku tych organizacji minęło wiele lat. Wyjątkowo żyzne sektory, takie jak ten, są często śladami dawnej działalności Terratechu.</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">SECTOR_FEATURE_ARTIFICIAL_FERTILITY</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">FEATURE</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">{Income}</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">{Income}</Data></Cell><Cell ss:Index="7"><Data ss:Type="String">Do not localize</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">REAPER_SPAWNER</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Reaper Bunker</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Bunkier kosiarza</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0" ss:Height="30"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">REAPER_SPAWNER</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">A reactivated bunker of deadly Reapers that now hunt aimlessly.[br/]If neglected, the Reapers will attack nearby colonies and armies.</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Uruchomiony na powrót bunkier śmiertelnie groźnych kosiarzy, którzy teraz polują bez większego sensu.[br/]Jeśli zostanie zignorowany, kosiarze zaczną atakować pobliskie kolonie i armie.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:Index="7"><Data ss:Type="String">Reapers are wildlife marauder units.</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">SECTOR_FEATURE_PARAGON_ESTATE</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Paragon Estate</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Posiadłość Wcielenia</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0" ss:Height="30"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">SECTOR_FEATURE_PARAGON_ESTATE</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">This sector houses the estate of the local governor, who assists the owner of the sector in diplomatic efforts.[br/]Grants {InfluenceIncome}[influence/] to the owner.</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">W tym sektorze znajduje się posiadłość miejscowego gubernatora, który wspiera właściciela sektora w działaniach dyplomatycznych.[br/]Daje właścicielowi {InfluenceIncome}[influence/].</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0" ss:Height="30"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">SECTOR_FEATURE_PARAGON_ESTATE</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">FLAVOUR</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Paragon Estates are extravagant displays of wealth, and this one is no different, though its lush gardens are littered with the decayed corpses of Paragon soldiers.</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Posiadłości Wcielenia są ekstrawaganckimi demonstracjami bogactwa, a ta jest pod tym względem typowa – choć jej bujne ogrody są zaścielone rozkładającymi się zwłokami żołnierzy Wcielenia.</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">SECTOR_FEATURE_PARAGON_ESTATE</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">FEATURE</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">{Income}</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">{Income}</Data></Cell><Cell ss:Index="7"><Data ss:Type="String">Do not localize</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">LIVESTOCK_SPAWNER</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Livestock Farms</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Fermy trzody chlewnej</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">LIVESTOCK_SPAWNER</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">A horrible site of experimentation and butchery filled with mutants.[br/]If neglected, the Mutants and Xenoplague will attack nearby colonies and armies.</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Straszliwe miejsce rzeźniczych eksperymentów, pełne mutantów.[br/]Jeśli je zlekceważysz, Ksenozaraza i mutanci będą atakować znajdujące się w pobliżu kolonie i armie.</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String"/></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String"/></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String"/></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String"/></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String"/></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String"/></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String"/></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String"/></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String"/></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String"/></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String"/></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String"/></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String"/></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String"/></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String"/></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String"/></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String"/></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String"/></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String"/></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String"/></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String"/></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String"/></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String"/></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String"/></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String"/></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String"/></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String"/></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String"/></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String"/></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String"/></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHe